data.description: Beautiful Lake view townhome 3/2 in exclusive gated community of Mediterranea has 1,746 square feet of living space. This 2 story home offers three bedrooms and two-and-a-half bathrooms. This open plan wraparound kitchen is fitted with modern stainless steel appliances. Plenty of space in dining room that flows right to a beautiful lake view. Upstairs, discover a Master Suite with a walk-in closet and in-suite bathroom with double-sink vanity as well as two generously sized bedrooms and a full bathroom.
